Description: Provides functions for the Redistributed-Beta (RB) distribution,
    including density, distribution function, random generation, raw moments,
    descriptive measures, parameter estimation by moments and maximum
    likelihood, model comparison, and bootstrap goodness-of-fit procedures for
    data supported on the unit interval.
